## 1. Purpose

This policy establishes {{ business_name }}'s position on copyright, intellectual property (IP), and related legal considerations arising from the use of AI tools. It addresses the ownership of AI-generated outputs, the risks of third-party IP infringement, trade secret protection, and disclosure obligations. This policy aligns with the **Copyright Act 1968 (Cth)**, the **Australian Consumer Law (ACL)**, and the **AI6 Guidance for AI Adoption** (October 2024).

