## 4. IP Ownership Rules

### 4.1 Ownership of AI Outputs

| Context | Owner | Conditions |
|---------|-------|------------|
| Employee using AI tools in the course of employment | {{ business_name }} | Subject to employment contract terms |
| Contractor using AI tools for {{ business_name }} | {{ business_name }} | Must be specified in contractor agreement with IP assignment clause |
| AI output generated using {{ business_name }}'s proprietary data | {{ business_name }} | Ensure vendor terms assign output IP to the customer |
| AI output generated using public data only | Uncertain | May not attract copyright; treat as unprotected |

### 4.2 Vendor IP Terms

Before using any AI tool for commercial output, verify:

- [ ] The vendor's terms of service assign IP rights in outputs to the customer ({{ business_name }})
- [ ] The vendor does not claim ownership or licence rights over outputs generated using {{ business_name }}'s data
- [ ] The vendor does not reserve the right to use {{ business_name }}'s outputs for model training without consent

