## 7. Disclosure Requirements

### 7.1 When Disclosure Is Required

{{ business_name }} will disclose the use of AI in the following circumstances:

| Circumstance | Disclosure Required | Method |
|--------------|--------------------|---------|
| Client deliverables containing AI-generated content | Yes | Written disclosure in deliverable or cover note |
| Marketing materials created with AI assistance | Yes (under ACL) | Disclosure in footer or metadata |
| Customer-facing AI interactions (chatbots, recommendations) | Yes | Clear notice at point of interaction |
| Regulatory filings or legal documents | Yes | Explicit statement in the document |
| Internal reports and analyses | Recommended | Notation in document header |

{% if ai_disclosure_to_customers %}
{{ business_name }} discloses AI use to customers. Ensure all customer-facing AI disclosures are consistent with this policy and reviewed quarterly.
{% else %}
**Recommendation:** {{ business_name }} should implement customer-facing AI disclosure practices, particularly for commercial deliverables and customer-facing AI interactions, to comply with ACL transparency expectations.
