### 7.2 Disclosure Wording

Recommended disclosure text for {{ business_name }}:

> *"This [content/document/output] was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence tools. All AI-generated content has been reviewed and verified by {{ business_name }} staff. {{ business_name }} takes responsibility for the accuracy and quality of this content."*

