## 8. AI-Assisted vs AI-Generated Content Guidelines

### 8.1 Staff Guidance

| Practice | Guidance |
|----------|----------|
| Use AI as a drafting tool | Write prompts with specific instructions; review and substantially modify outputs |
| Add original analysis | Layer human expertise, judgment, and original analysis on top of AI drafts |
| Select and arrange | Exercise creative judgment in selecting which AI outputs to use and how to arrange them |
| Document your contribution | Keep records of how you directed, modified, and refined AI outputs |
| Do not submit AI outputs as-is | All AI outputs must be reviewed, edited, and verified before use |

